{
  "meta": {
    "voice": null,
    "language": null,
    "rate": "1",
    "pitch": "0",
    "generatedAt": "2026-03-26T01:13:11.149Z"
  },
  "items": [
    {
      "kind": "title",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "我是谁？你是谁？——学习谈论人",
      "file": "zh-cn-5be42a8b27d2ea222654de1093761e0611fec3b9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "title",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Who I Am and Who You Are – Learning to Talk About People",
      "file": "en-us-f2ea1a54488b4a48dc2cbf6b91d3c04382615b2d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "介绍",
      "file": "zh-cn-b2f1469ad17de782fee6350f41c7a626f7a92005.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Introduction",
      "file": "en-us-ddc4642e5ae6a7ebd9c4918c52a19699a895de75.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "在这节课中，我们要学习如何介绍自己，也学习如何谈论别人。",
      "file": "zh-cn-baff5949b750e724677708fc1f59b377b09eb54e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "In this lesson, we will learn how to say who we are and talk about other people.",
      "file": "en-us-b6af15c3cfd0b933504bbf79cfdfdd709eca500e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "我们会用简单的句子来说名字和感受。",
      "file": "zh-cn-6e5fdf14b244280903ff955df5a983d43ee943e8.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "We will use simple sentences to say names and how someone feels.",
      "file": "en-us-6bf14654520033b18e711d4e0ea2ce70481bfe4d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "还有一件很重要的事：上帝知道每一个人的名字。",
      "file": "zh-cn-2883523d06857bdb5bacb21073a629c0cac3aec8.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "And we will remember something very important: God knows every person by name.",
      "file": "en-us-c5e07b9eae9501364dd915bfef24420f902b1f64.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "1. 说自己",
      "file": "zh-cn-2f5d3be11d4d0ae0701542b10eebc2c4f02ff417.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "1. Talking about myself",
      "file": "en-us-a12dd7491ae90321b1220517c54e88dab184ce4c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "当我们说自己时，我们用一种特别的说法。",
      "file": "zh-cn-ff1ac9cf667c28361f0ccd1c174c8d960a46a4d7.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "When we talk about ourselves, we use a special form.",
      "file": "en-us-2b073f31ab8f554a23194d067e8190b3460be9d2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "我们可以说自己的名字，也可以说自己的感觉。",
      "file": "zh-cn-2055234b42befd8f687f8816f39c867009e204d4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "With this form, we can say our name or how we feel.",
      "file": "en-us-21d937c6431cd161d398e80bb46317d34e9515be.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "看看这些例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-57438f0cd4ebf5a7c64008ae41ec96daa8f4a29e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "See the examples:",
      "file": "en-us-e86b0eaca450d6b3cd52d307fa78ab63a59ddbe2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am a boy.",
      "file": "en-us-2ea7a194959761fc6819b0a71918a66db527430d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am happy.",
      "file": "en-us-23939b7341e0b2db15f437958c508b0842216b70.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am Moses.",
      "file": "en-us-5fd7218dba7b66e228565abe8c016114d4e7ab2c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "这里，这个人在说自己。",
      "file": "zh-cn-0874654d3abbc3a3b533c9a3ddbc8efa5b1acb76.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Here, the person is talking about themselves.",
      "file": "en-us-3023e093dcdaebf3a43c56e61b732c66ca4f626c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "就像说：“我”。",
      "file": "zh-cn-a630caeed6f14a2e0f8c1df23133a977122faa31.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "It is like saying: I.",
      "file": "en-us-886701a3763ebd3826fb24852f45cee37606ec44.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "2. 对别人说话",
      "file": "zh-cn-99d70ce8a8b3baf213d7001571b7da7d6db5a3b5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "2. Talking to another person",
      "file": "en-us-18851b1a8429e91fbb743e94437439b812127fe2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "当我们直接和别人说话时，我们用另一种说法。",
      "file": "zh-cn-37dbfaf1916c43a6d8159cdb9c8cce724c84973c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "When we speak directly to someone, we use another form.",
      "file": "en-us-97dccd3ca5536ea19c2d1123deab58e4a4e30238.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "当我们看着那个人并对他说话时，就用这种说法。",
      "file": "zh-cn-02297ddb7523df2cedd73bc3f4bed45c94aac95e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "We use it when we look at the person and talk to them.",
      "file": "en-us-d284a9a1e59e44832f0ff7927fc0e9d6c7558dc8.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "看看这些例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-57438f0cd4ebf5a7c64008ae41ec96daa8f4a29e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "See the examples:",
      "file": "en-us-e86b0eaca450d6b3cd52d307fa78ab63a59ddbe2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are a boy.",
      "file": "en-us-d77d87e8e23a7d0f9fa4de519606bdb500208fe4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are a girl.",
      "file": "en-us-4057e5dd51af2766d75664e2de122f5da27990c9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are happy.",
      "file": "en-us-d88c326c1e116ceabac6175587976a0f555d96a0.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are special.",
      "file": "en-us-bd168e4be2ccb03a768f5e99a6affc68421f8f80.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "这里，我们是在和别人说话。",
      "file": "zh-cn-478dcdecab0a636b6984a4ab1fe11d5461baad00.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Here, we are talking to someone.",
      "file": "en-us-d67882b8c8d9a58856e17377cff5b3a32e37cefa.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "就像说：“你”。",
      "file": "zh-cn-868e83b82e7d43708220c69981bc1ffd6c5d669b.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "It is like saying: you.",
      "file": "en-us-8d3f124aa46d0eacf90373812fa4e630b0945598.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "3. 说一个男孩或男人",
      "file": "zh-cn-f9f9bedb8ee65438d8fa6fae9ef4d209de49b84b.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "3. Talking about a boy or a man",
      "file": "en-us-63b52f4d13ad9a0caeca42af488f47e605a28ce6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "现在，想一想一个不在对话中的男孩。",
      "file": "zh-cn-97a39cf5b3f2820d4a26a83d15c72ef9f44b45e9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Now, imagine we are talking about a boy who is not in the conversation.",
      "file": "en-us-ca663d0193008c55159b8b72539a768b90acc626.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "他没有在说话，我们也不是直接对他说话。",
      "file": "zh-cn-96dc85f2a968cbdfdd1fe6e9455bd9d4fbaed891.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is not speaking and we are not talking to him directly.",
      "file": "en-us-f27c9ee328afc273b74c52e55a6f97450a18a316.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "我们是在对别人说他的情况。",
      "file": "zh-cn-8fbbcc36a28b7eb0cdce7199390e94582ffc47b7.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "We are just talking about him to another person.",
      "file": "en-us-aef94edf5f9a2ce28315c2a91b174d18ab866aef.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "看看这些例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-57438f0cd4ebf5a7c64008ae41ec96daa8f4a29e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "See the examples:",
      "file": "en-us-e86b0eaca450d6b3cd52d307fa78ab63a59ddbe2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is a boy.",
      "file": "en-us-2a2632a545de1823da43afd6efaf7a9bdde88adf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is happy.",
      "file": "en-us-82d5659b428ca8187f1b62cd7b1c594773f693e2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is Moses.",
      "file": "en-us-1875dbfb2e551e944cb3613e86530d6cc03308b8.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "这里，我们在说一个男孩或男人。",
      "file": "zh-cn-32a8df1d1a57fd0dd320af18420bb8aca58f6f20.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Here, we are talking about a boy or a man.",
      "file": "en-us-d2446f94cd5c8e99c31d773be4ec137f3eccb813.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "就像指着他，然后告诉别人。",
      "file": "zh-cn-d87f4e0030ae8055ab57d22d49dba59846026d36.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "It is like pointing to him and telling something.",
      "file": "en-us-971f789f9248667ff5601c4b451a23ca5a4a4768.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "4. 说一个女孩或女人",
      "file": "zh-cn-d7bfc8262c10bfdc70aca2d7511636793d48d4a1.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "4. Talking about a girl or a woman",
      "file": "en-us-2928311111f0c8234c4ed787b45727aa6b7eb9d9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "我们也可以说一个女孩或女人。",
      "file": "zh-cn-36726863fb74104f1bc5a11ca303d6ba83b0206c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "We can also talk about a girl or a woman.",
      "file": "en-us-97cd6fc43619a005ee07d6e18e29bb750214923b.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "她没有在说话，我们也不是直接对她说话。",
      "file": "zh-cn-73471f14feab7a5c5b146d50b830004d033a8366.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Just like before, she is not speaking and we are not talking to her directly.",
      "file": "en-us-bca256274bf143b543da2a19a681bce2f5883c73.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "我们是在说她的情况。",
      "file": "zh-cn-d83450ac7690f0cf8ae3726ed797303958e1ab24.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "We are talking about her.",
      "file": "en-us-cea4656f37534286c5381eff9c3d315ce221a0ed.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "看看这些例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-57438f0cd4ebf5a7c64008ae41ec96daa8f4a29e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "See the examples:",
      "file": "en-us-e86b0eaca450d6b3cd52d307fa78ab63a59ddbe2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "She is a girl.",
      "file": "en-us-30ddae33c2bccaca73a4be47e7712fd4c9bfcf94.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "She is happy.",
      "file": "en-us-d1b3d3c880ee376906cd771d820b9756e0aed280.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "She is Hannah.",
      "file": "en-us-d1fcfedd52306f6c11995ac3e30ad2bbc7bf56f6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "这里，我们在说一个女孩或女人。",
      "file": "zh-cn-1a79179981ad3b9a3092fceaddd6630fd02f33bf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Here, we are talking about a girl or a woman.",
      "file": "en-us-557338fd540294c4f62a0380eab0bb726cf1dad4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "就像指着她，然后告诉别人。",
      "file": "zh-cn-ba32cad8baa1b8986b4319ec04ba93c12014cf1e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "It is like pointing to her and telling something.",
      "file": "en-us-7282ef6dddf24ea6c25c3b292a99e552f4eff020.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "5. 上帝认识你",
      "file": "zh-cn-429aac74ef4156b8f52ca13fdea28c92ca82df84.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "5. God knows you",
      "file": "en-us-0df08ba78ecc3cc8c934c02a47dde7b40dd1c956.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "上帝知道每一个人的名字。",
      "file": "zh-cn-7c1b7a1dd3de46c1af6c8e2d1c64e50c3333b0c5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "God knows every person by name.",
      "file": "en-us-bcef82b34bc452f2185c10145f2180c2cf749014.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "你很重要，你很特别。",
      "file": "zh-cn-ec42dd46095ad7c0c5a6ef70a5c932cf9254ac06.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are important and special.",
      "file": "en-us-2a95145c0656668a301ed7aa59c259a140977cdd.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "看看这些例子：",
      "file": "zh-cn-57438f0cd4ebf5a7c64008ae41ec96daa8f4a29e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "See the examples:",
      "file": "en-us-e86b0eaca450d6b3cd52d307fa78ab63a59ddbe2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am special.",
      "file": "en-us-30659168470ea344e663e832d4071108350f3afd.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are special.",
      "file": "en-us-bd168e4be2ccb03a768f5e99a6affc68421f8f80.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is special.",
      "file": "en-us-16532c2721b9ac71a837d574e6544ce38cdaa297.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "She is special.",
      "file": "en-us-5c8404f35b519d351ea9495b1ec21edc456b1f43.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "每一个人都很特别。",
      "file": "zh-cn-1d27e9f6c0574f3b6cd03e6322146e6a35b7e49e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "All people are special.",
      "file": "en-us-3bf1c88b4de9057ee558e9c39d9aa19d5ce28396.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "上帝认识每一个人。",
      "file": "zh-cn-4db883fbbbbbead3a148eacaa37d7b63df684570.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "God knows each one of them.",
      "file": "en-us-2b0df657ba37a2492b85992db8f6ff1dc9bc254d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "总结",
      "file": "zh-cn-ac47ec5504b1af7466662f04b2343ee4c68813ed.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Conclusion",
      "file": "en-us-e1f195b655ae7e4263baa0a54dd91effd6a06a28.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "在这节课中，我们学习了如何介绍自己和谈论别人。",
      "file": "zh-cn-5d3879685a57643ae56014f109269d424a881899.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "In this lesson, we learned how to talk about ourselves and other people.",
      "file": "en-us-830f5e6213023de6284a46a8c5fd1b0e20549e7b.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "我们学习了和别人说话，也学习了谈论别人。",
      "file": "zh-cn-d05926824427e39740d7cf1b422afad67ad94140.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "We learned to speak to someone and to talk about someone.",
      "file": "en-us-eed54de021bbd68efcf4894e57cef1f50ee9a7e2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "现在你可以用简单的句子来介绍自己和别人了。",
      "file": "zh-cn-01afcb6e5069ad05c6745aaa580d3ebae8d01ba5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "Now you can say simple things about yourself and others.",
      "file": "en-us-4b3e08636ad0aecd9a656b4cbf2392fa0f0a30e8.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "cmn-CN",
      "voice": "cmn-CN-Standard-A",
      "text": "记住：上帝知道你的名字，你很特别。",
      "file": "zh-cn-f3f1113370f40b65d91b5b67feb966a29860a5d8.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "And remember: God knows you by name and you are special.",
      "file": "en-us-b2f5aed4f81d4be82fd27757e4256808d5f37d0a.mp3"
    }
  ]
}